gcpb - Git Cherry Pick on Branch

USAGE:
    gcpb <target-branch> <source-reference>

DESCRIPTION:
    Checkout the specified branch before cherry-picking the requested
    changes, pushing, and restoring the original branch.

ARGUMENTS:
    target-branch
        Branch to apply the cherry-pick on

    source-reference
        Source branch, tag, or git commit to cherry pick

EXAMPLES:
    gcpb main feature-branch
    gcpb develop abc123
    gcpb release v1.0.0